Siap. Berikut cara paling cepat membuat wallet EVM secara lokal.

Node.js (ethers v6):
const { Wallet } = require("ethers");

const wallet = Wallet.createRandom();
console.log("Address:", wallet.address);
console.log("Private Key:", wallet.privateKey);
console.log("Mnemonic:", wallet.mnemonic.phrase);

Langkah pakai:
1. Buat folder baru
2. Jalankan:
   npm init -y
   npm install ethers
3. Simpan kode di file misalnya create-wallet.js
4. Jalankan:
   node create-wallet.js

Versi yang simpan ke file .json lokal:
const { Wallet } = require("ethers");
const fs = require("fs");

const wallet = Wallet.createRandom();

const data = {
  address: wallet.address,
  privateKey: wallet.privateKey,
  mnemonic: wallet.mnemonic.phrase
};

fs.writeFileSync("wallet.json", JSON.stringify(data, null, 2));
console.log("Wallet disimpan ke wallet.json");

